headline: Is Texas Instruments (TXN) Pricing In Too Much Growth After Recent Share Price Strength
summary: Wondering if Texas Instruments at around US$196.59 is offering solid value or asking too much? This article is designed to help you make sense of the price tag before you make your next move. The stock has recently posted returns of 2.6% over 7 days, 11.1% over 30 days, 10.7% year to date, 8.5% over 1 year, 23.5% over 3 years, and 30.6% over 5 years.
